sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant ListPage as OperationTasks.tsx
    participant CreateModal as OperationTaskCreateModal
    participant EditPage as OperationTaskEdit.tsx
    participant API as api/operations.ts
    participant Router as routers/operations.py
    participant Repo as operations_repository.py
    participant DB as SQLite

    %% ---- 列表加载 ----
    Note over ListPage,DB: === 列表加载与筛选 ===
    User->>ListPage: 进入 /operations/tasks
    ListPage->>API: GET /api/operations/tasks?search=&type=&enabled=&run_status=
    API->>Router: HTTP GET
    Router->>Repo: list_all(filters)
    Repo->>DB: SELECT * FROM operation_tasks WHERE ... ORDER BY created_at DESC
    DB-->>Repo: rows
    Repo-->>Router: (items, total)
    Router-->>API: OperationTaskResponse[]
    API-->>ListPage: OperationTask[]
    ListPage->>ListPage: render 卡片网格

    %% ---- Switch 切换 ----
    Note over ListPage,DB: === Switch 启用切换 ===
    User->>ListPage: 点击 Switch
    ListPage->>ListPage: 乐观更新 UI
    ListPage->>API: PATCH /api/operations/tasks/:id/toggle
    API->>Router: HTTP PATCH
    Router->>Repo: toggle(task_id)
    Repo->>DB: UPDATE operation_tasks SET enabled = NOT enabled, updated_at = now
    DB-->>Repo: ok
    Repo-->>Router: updated task dict
    Router-->>API: OperationTaskResponse
    API-->>ListPage: updated task (reconcile)

    %% ---- 创建任务 4 步 Stepper ----
    Note over CreateModal,DB: === 创建运营任务（4 步 Stepper） ===

    User->>ListPage: 点击"创建运营任务"
    ListPage->>CreateModal: open (step=1)

    Note over CreateModal: Step 1: 选择任务类型
    User->>CreateModal: 选择"群发任务"
    CreateModal->>CreateModal: step=2

    Note over CreateModal: Step 2: 设置任务参数
    User->>CreateModal: 填写名称/渠道/会话类型/内容块/托管

    CreateModal->>CreateModal: step=3
    Note over CreateModal: Step 3: 选择运营对象

    CreateModal->>API: GET /api/operations/targets/sessions?account_id=&search=
    API->>Router: HTTP GET
    Router->>Repo: list_sessions_for_targeting(filters)
    Repo->>DB: SELECT cs.* FROM channel_sessions cs WHERE ...
    DB-->>Repo: rows
    Repo-->>Router: list[dict]
    Router-->>API: TargetSessionResponse[]
    API-->>CreateModal: sessions list

    User->>CreateModal: 勾选目标会话 (checkbox)
    CreateModal->>CreateModal: step=4

    Note over CreateModal: Step 4: 设置运行时间
    User->>CreateModal: 选择频率"单次" + 运行时间 + 生效区间
    User->>CreateModal: 点击"创建任务"

    CreateModal->>API: POST /api/operations/tasks (完整 body)
    API->>Router: HTTP POST + OperationTaskCreateRequest
    Router->>Repo: create(data) with transaction
    Repo->>DB: BEGIN
    Repo->>DB: INSERT INTO operation_tasks (...)
    Repo->>DB: INSERT INTO operation_task_targets (...) × N
    Repo->>DB: COMMIT
    DB-->>Repo: ok
    Repo-->>Router: task dict
    Router-->>API: 201 + OperationTaskResponse
    API-->>CreateModal: success
    CreateModal->>CreateModal: close + toast "运营任务创建成功"
    CreateModal-->>ListPage: onCreated() → 刷新列表

    %% ---- 编辑页 ----
    Note over EditPage,DB: === 编辑任务（独立路由 + 三 Tab） ===

    User->>ListPage: 点击任务卡"编辑"
    ListPage->>EditPage: navigate(/operations/tasks/:id/edit)

    EditPage->>API: GET /api/operations/tasks/:id
    API->>Router: HTTP GET
    Router->>Repo: get(task_id)
    Repo->>DB: SELECT * FROM operation_tasks WHERE id=?
    DB-->>Repo: row
    Repo-->>Router: task dict
    Router-->>API: OperationTaskResponse
    API-->>EditPage: OperationTask

    EditPage->>API: GET /api/operations/tasks/:id/targets
    API->>Router: HTTP GET
    Router->>Repo: list_targets(task_id)
    Repo->>DB: SELECT ott.*, cs.name FROM operation_task_targets ott JOIN channel_sessions cs ON cs.id = ott.session_id WHERE ott.task_id=?
    DB-->>Repo: rows
    Repo-->>Router: list[dict]
    Router-->>API: OperationTaskTargetResponse[]
    API-->>EditPage: targets

    Note over EditPage: Tab 1: 任务参数（回填）
    User->>EditPage: 修改内容块/托管机器人
    User->>EditPage: 切换到 Tab 2: 运营对象

    EditPage->>API: GET /api/operations/targets/sessions
    API->>Router: HTTP GET
    Router->>Repo: list_sessions_for_targeting()
    Repo->>DB: SELECT * FROM channel_sessions
    DB-->>Repo: rows
    Repo-->>Router: list[dict]
    Router-->>API: TargetSessionResponse[]
    API-->>EditPage: sessions (标记已选)

    User->>EditPage: 增删目标会话
    User->>EditPage: 切换到 Tab 3: 任务时间
    User->>EditPage: 修改频率/时间/生效区间
    User->>EditPage: 点击"保存"

    EditPage->>API: PUT /api/operations/tasks/:id (任务参数+时间)
    API->>Router: HTTP PUT + OperationTaskUpdateRequest
    Router->>Repo: update(task_id, data)
    Repo->>DB: UPDATE operation_tasks SET ...
    DB-->>Repo: ok

    EditPage->>API: PUT /api/operations/tasks/:id/targets (新目标列表)
    API->>Router: HTTP PUT
    Router->>Repo: set_targets(task_id, targets)
    Repo->>DB: BEGIN; DELETE FROM operation_task_targets WHERE task_id=?; INSERT INTO ...; COMMIT
    DB-->>Repo: ok
    Router-->>API: success
    EditPage->>EditPage: toast "保存成功"
    EditPage->>ListPage: navigate('/operations/tasks')

    %% ---- 运营记录（P0 toast 占位） ----
    Note over ListPage: === 运营记录（P0 toast 占位） ===
    User->>ListPage: 点击任务卡"运营记录"
    ListPage->>ListPage: toast("查看运营记录") 占位
